OL,3,CFrom increased chance of heatwaves to
OL,4,Cmore rain: What does summer have in
OL,5,Cstore?
OL,7,FAfter the record-breaking May
OL,8,Fheatwave, with the highest ever
OL,9,Ftemperatures recorded in the UK so
OL,10,Fearly in the year, what's in store as
OL,11,Fwe slide into June and the rest of the
OL,12,Fsummer?
OL,14,FThe May heat was remarkable, with
OL,15,Ftemperatures well over 30C for a run
OL,16,Fof five days coinciding with the late
OL,17,Flong weekend and the school holidays -
OL,18,Ffor once!
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780567570
OL,3,CFrom increased chance of heatwaves to
OL,4,Cmore rain: What does summer have in
OL,5,Cstore?
OL,7,FJust as school returns and June
OL,8,Fbegins, we'll see a step back to
OL,9,Ffresher, cooler air and some notable
OL,10,Frain. Temperatures are up to 15C lower
OL,11,Ffor some of us.
OL,13,FHow long will we keep this cooler,
OL,14,Frainy weather?
OL,16,FWith a shift in air mass, the return
OL,17,Fof our usual prevailing westerly winds
OL,18,Fand unstable air in the upper
OL,19,Fatmosphere, we can expect rain to be
OL,20,Fsweeping from west to east.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780567570
OL,3,CFrom increased chance of heatwaves to
OL,4,Cmore rain: What does summer have in
OL,5,Cstore?
OL,7,FIt will bring some lively blustery,
OL,8,Fthundery downpours with a chance of
OL,9,Fhail in places.
OL,11,FFor some, the rain is much needed
OL,12,Fafter a dry spell, but in this case,
OL,13,Fwhen it rains, it pours!
OL,15,FTogether with the often heavy rain,
OL,16,Fthere'll be brisk and gusty winds into
OL,17,FThursday.
OL,19,FIt's actually unseasonably windy for
OL,20,Fthe time of year, more so in the south
OL,21,Fand west.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780567570
OL,3,CFrom increased chance of heatwaves to
OL,4,Cmore rain: What does summer have in
OL,5,Cstore?
OL,7,FThis will make it feel much cooler
OL,8,Fthan expected - especially after the
OL,9,Fheat of last week.
OL,11,FWe're likely to get a drier respite on
OL,12,FFriday with a little more sunshine.
OL,14,FBut another area of rain will move
OL,15,Fthrough many areas into the first
OL,16,Fstages of Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780567570
OL,3,CFrom increased chance of heatwaves to
OL,4,Cmore rain: What does summer have in
OL,5,Cstore?
OL,7,FFrom the latest charts, the weather is
OL,8,Flooking changeable into the weekend
OL,9,Fand beyond with temperatures lower
OL,10,Fthan those during the end of the week
OL,11,Fand some rain, longer downpours and
OL,12,Fsome blustery winds for the time of
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FWhen will the drier, sunnier weather
OL,16,Freturn?
OL,18,FRight now, the second half of June
OL,19,Flooks more favourable with the weather
OL,20,Fsettling down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780567570
OL,3,CFrom increased chance of heatwaves to
OL,4,Cmore rain: What does summer have in
OL,5,Cstore?
OL,7,FWarmth and sunshine are set to return
OL,8,Fas high pressure re-establishes
OL,9,Fitself, together with lighter winds
OL,10,Fand drier conditions.
OL,12,FWe can expect temperatures to be much
OL,13,Fbetter than this week - but not quite
OL,14,Fthe heat we had a few days ago.
OL,16,FSunny skies will make all the
OL,17,Fdifference, even more so this time of
OL,18,Fyear!
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
