PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780567570
OL,3,CFrom increased chance of heatwaves to
OL,4,Cmore rain: What does summer have in
OL,5,Cstore?
OL,7,FThe sun will have more strength, with
OL,8,Fdaylight hours almost at their longest
OL,9,Fpoint - the Summer Solstice, the
OL,10,Flongest day of the year, is not too
OL,11,Ffar away.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FHow is the rest of the summer looking?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
