PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780567570
OL,3,CFrom increased chance of heatwaves to
OL,4,Cmore rain: What does summer have in
OL,5,Cstore?
OL,7,FAt a very distant glance, July looks
OL,8,Fwarmer, with a chance of some hotter
OL,9,Fweather - but at this stage, it is
OL,10,Fstill changeable.
OL,12,FThere are indications of August
OL,13,Flooking a little more stable - or
OL,14,Fconsistent. But the details will
OL,15,Fbecome much clearer in the coming
OL,16,Fweeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
