PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780567570
OL,3,CFrom increased chance of heatwaves to
OL,4,Cmore rain: What does summer have in
OL,5,Cstore?
OL,7,FThe Met Office three-month (summer)
OL,8,Fforecast indicates that a hotter than
OL,9,Faverage summer is twice as likely this
OL,10,Fyear, but this is purely statistically
OL,11,F- or probability - based.
OL,13,FThis brings an increased chance of
OL,14,Fheatwaves, but with this comes a
OL,15,Fchance of higher humidity and
OL,16,Fthunderstorms. That means chances of a
OL,17,Fwetter season are also higher than
OL,18,Fnormal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780567570
OL,3,CFrom increased chance of heatwaves to
OL,4,Cmore rain: What does summer have in
OL,5,Cstore?
OL,7,FOverall, there is a higher chance of
OL,8,Fthis summer being nearer average when
OL,9,Fit comes to high temperatures and
OL,10,Frainfall.
OL,12,FHow will it shape up in comparison to
OL,13,Fsummers past?
OL,15,FLast summer was exceptional for its
OL,16,Fconsistent heat. It was characterised
OL,17,Fby several heatwaves and a stretch of
OL,18,Fhot sunny days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
